Fun Faces lets you play with your phone and change the eyes, mouth, and background color easily.

* Drag around eyes & mouth
* Change eyes by flinging them off screen
* Change mouth by flinging off screen
* Change background color by tapping the bottom

* Hundreds of possible face combinations
* Entertain kids with silly faces
* Have fun with different faces

Fun Faces is designed, built, and maintained in California. We'd love to know how we can improve your experience, 

Improvement idea: remove the text from the bottom for screenshots or have a way to save the images otherwise so that users could build their own wallpapers